1       ST Introduction (ASE_INT)

                 1.1 ST Reference and TOE Reference
                      Table 1. ST Reference and TOE reference
                      Title          JCOP 4.7 SE051 Security Target Lite
                      Version        Revision 1.3
                      Date           30 June 2020
                      Product Type   Java Card
