Software Library RSA2048/4096 v2.03.008, EC v2.03.008, SHA-2 v1.01, SCL v2.02.010
libraries, and Toolbox v2.03.008, as well as with speci    FCS.COP.1[HW_DES] now claims compliance to NIST SP800-67
